14:["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4","children":"Kalkulyatordan qanday foydalanish"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-sm sm:prose-base max-w-none text-muted-foreground space-y-4","children":[["$","div","0",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Kalkulyator qanday ishlaydi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Yoqilg'i sarfi kalkulyatori sayohat narxini va 100 km yo'lga benzin yoki gaz o'rtacha sarfini hisoblaydi. O'zbekistonda yoqilg'i bozori metan (siqilgan tabiiy gaz) ning keng tarqalganligi bilan ajralib turadi — yengil avtomobillarning taxminan 70% gaz uskunasi bilan jihozlangan. Joriy yoqilg'i narxlari: AI-91 — ~12 500 so'm/l, AI-95 — ~14 500 so'm/l, propan — ~7 000-8 000 so'm/l, metan — ~5 200 so'm/m³. AI-80 benzini 2025-yil 1-dekabrdan ishlab chiqarishdan chiqarilgan."}]]}]]}],["$","div","1",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash formulasi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Hisoblash formulasi: sayohat narxi = (masofa / 100) × 100 km ga sarf × litr (yoki m³) narxi. O'zbekistonda mashhur avtomobillarning o'rtacha sarfi: Chevrolet Cobalt — 7–8 l/100 km, Chevrolet Nexia — 8–9 l/100 km, Chevrolet Tracker — 9–10 l/100 km. Metanda xuddi shu modellarning sarfi: 6–9 m³/100 km. Shahar ichida haydash, konditsioner ishlatish va ortiqcha yuklashda sarf oshadi."}]]}]]}],["$","div","2",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash misoli"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Misol: Toshkent — Samarqand marshruti (300 km) Chevrolet Cobalt da AI-91 benzinda 8 l/100 km sarfda 300 000 so'mga tushadi. Metanda xuddi shu sayohat atigi 109 200 so'm — 2,7 marta tejash. Har kungi ishga sayohatlarda (kuniga 30 km, 22 ish kuni) oylik benzin xarajatlari taxminan 660 000 so'm, metanda esa atigi 240 000 so'm."}]]}]]}],["$","div","3",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Nimalarni hisobga olish kerak"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Metanga o'tish — O'zbekistondagi avtomobilist uchun eng foydali qarorlardan biri. Gaz uskunasini o'rnatish narxi 3–5 mln so'm bo'lib, o'rtacha yurishda 6–12 oyda o'zini oqlaydi. Mamlakatda rivojlangan gaz to'ldirish stansiyalari (AGNKS) tarmog'i mavjud, ayniqsa asosiy shaharlararo trassalar bo'ylab. Biroq, gazdagi dvigatel quvvati 10–15% ga kamayishini hisobga olish kerak."}]]}]]}],["$","div","4",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Foydali maslahatlar"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Bizning yoqilg'i sarfi kalkulyatorimiz har qanday marshrut uchun xarajatlarni aniq hisoblash imkonini beradi: masofani, avtomobilingizning sarfini va yoqilg'i turini kiriting — sayohat narxini bir zumda bilib olasiz. Kalkulyator shuningdek benzin va metan xarajatlarini solishtiradi, bu sizning aniq foydalanish rejimingiz uchun gazga o'tish foydasini baholashga yordam beradi."}]]}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-8 space-y-6","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-foreground","children":"Ma'lumotnoma va tariflar"}],[["$","div","0",{"className":"overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-border","children":["$","table",null,{"className":"w-full text-sm","children":["$L19","$L1a","$L1b"]}]}]]]}],"$L1c","$L1d"]}]
